title: Episode 287: Who’s Ashley!? (Feat. Yung Bleu)
itunes:title: Episode 287: Who’s Ashley!? (Feat. Yung Bleu)
description:
Hip Hop/R&B Artist Yung Bleu is here to promote his upcoming single and album “Ghetto Love Birds.” Yung Bleu opens up and gets personal about a handful of topics including: the lack of love he received from his parents, how it’s shaped him as a man today, landing the feature of “You’re Mines Still’ with Drake, and much more. Yung Bleu addresses why he dyed his hair such a loud color, and he even admits that his music starts fights between him and his girl. Enjoy!
